description:
eBay tricks and tips and beginners (Newbies course)

This course is designed to teach you new ways to make money on eBay. It will cover a lot of basic and advanced concepts in simple short lectures, and teach you a few ways you can profit. This course includes practical examples as well. 

As an eBay Powerseller, I have significant experience with everything to do with eBay. This course will give you a taste of some of my methods for how to make money on eBay. In this course, I will cover some of those methods. To learn more, you have to buy the full course.
title: eBay tricks and tips for beginners
